{
  "stem": "15115.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I told you before, that we had a lot of paper money, but it became useless.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, the paper money became like you-- instead of it being 10 drachmas a loaf of bread, it was 10,000 drachmas a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were in bad shape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I started going into the black market business, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'd buy cigarettes and sell them in the market, the black market.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I used to go to the Union Station where the new German soldiers used to arrive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I used to trade cigarettes with different-- they'd give me a lighter or cheese-- what do you call them, those cheese cubes?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I used to do quite a bit with them. 12:00 noon used to be the train in, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This I used to speak a few words of German, and I used to get all-- they used to like Greek cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to have the most worst cigarettes to us, [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Extra ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Palock, ?] which was the cheapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was very extra, which the Germans didn't know, so I used to change with them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that continued for a few months, I was doing this kind of business.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then at night I used to go to different taverns and buy German marks and change them with Greek denominations, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anything that I can make a buck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But towards the end, it got really, really tough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So what do we do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I start selling stuff in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "First of all, I sold my mother's sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We got some money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, my money-- my mother had two big thick gold bracelets, really heavy, that was from her dowry when she got married.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
